title: Why MrBeast has MULTIPLE YouTube Channels
description: In the second episode of Creator Economics, Reed and Blake discuss Platform Diversification. The ability to create effective content on multiple platforms is the most powerful skill a creator can build.
dc:creator: Reed Duchscher and Blake Robbins
